tweet: This is the last week of Lung Cancer Awareness Month! Our final facts for this month are about lung cancer survivors.  Early detection can be done using a low dose CT scan and can decrease cancer mortality rates by 14-20% in high risk populations.  https://t.co/FolnnufQ0C
